<section xml:id="sec-hyperbolas" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Hyperbolas</title>
            <p>By the end of this section, you should</p>
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <p>know the geometric definition of a hyperbola.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>know the meaning of the center, vertices, foci and transverse axis of a hyperbola.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>be able to find equation of a hyperbola whose transverse axis is horizontal or vertical.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>be able to identify equations representing sec-hyperbolas.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>be able to find the center, vertices, foci, and asymptotes of a hyperbola and sketch the hyperbola.</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                
            </p>
